{"tid":1708950,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人 一日唔正式宣戰","createTime":"2019-11-11T18:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T00:12:18.000Z","uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4209b2b2b75ba5ee94ba375321986db52c09f883","tid":1708950,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:21:33.000Z","msg":"只會令更多 手足無辜被捕<br />\n<br />\n團火唔應該係咁用 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟出面仲有幾多人 唔覺得係打緊仗？<br />\n戰事的確展開左 只係我地一直都係挨打一方 無能力反抗"},{"pid":"35f0d6b0d2e53b1a3d7656d256e8b3889e3bf683","tid":1708950,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:22:36.000Z","msg":"tg 450度 根本就係毒到仆街 生化武器<br />\n無知港豬 以為縮得就縮 死左都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"af8fb8810fe198a12a2c58207b7d6fe1b830b62d","tid":1708950,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:30:20.000Z","msg":"其實知係打仗<br />\n但敵人係全球最黑暗人數最多既支那黨軍<br />\n而唔係香港差佬黑警<br />\npopo係狗無錯，共狗而已<br />\n香港人係遲早對支那宣戰既<br />\n不過呢樣真係要諗清楚先"},{"pid":"30ec1048461973aae05fb781f6c958374e440a0e","tid":1708950,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:30:50.000Z","msg":"個啲係軍人黎 唔撚係差人 你地譴責佢 無撚用<br />\n軍人戰犯罪行 係必然 , 姦淫擄掠 濫殺無辜<br />\n要發洩係低智前線到 徒勞 佢地都係盲目服從頂上柯打<br />\n <br />\n反而小心啲  武力唔對等 唔好搞咁多對抗 <br />\n等待真正既日子來臨 可以'玉帛相對' <br />\n⋯ <br />\n就係不嬲都提倡既升級"},{"pid":"255b1f4d578670492833a1dba305b292fb520ca5","tid":1708950,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"冇美國參戰係贏唔到"},{"pid":"5d8d0b88e2d8e7d4bafa6f55cad75ead89a31ede","tid":1708950,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"有軍火先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c92d6ca7f256be2173ca98a21b0a024f1419a51","tid":1708950,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"講"},{"pid":"033f8b263aa